short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use Notion as a CMS for your Laravel app.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
⚠️ This extension includes paid plans. 

Nortta monitors changes you make to your Notion pages, parse Notion blocks into plain HTML, and syncs them with your Laravel app. 

To activate your extension, create an account on www.nortta.com and follow the setup wizard.
